{"tid":946365,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【HMV清盤】CD Warehouse：唱片市場健康　生存睇本事","createTime":"2018-12-18T12:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T17:09:31.000Z","uid":17646,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6ff44650f9ac31b1d7bff59a172798548328181b","tid":946365,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2223143/org/25adbff5c81d8a08cda60a6bd77fa2bb.jpg/B9zaW8ZeA-XcEg17fmJsupyW3BcaBcVEhUNUwoVDVMI?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2223143%2Forg%2F25adbff5c81d8a08cda60a6bd77fa2bb.jpg%2FB9zaW8ZeA-XcEg17fmJsupyW3BcaBcVEhUNUwoVDVMI%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=60a0a955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHMV決定自願清盤，極可能是繼今年6月全線結業的「香港唱片」（Hong Kong Record）後，另一間走進歷史的連鎖唱片店。<br />\n<br />\n隨着一間又一間老牌唱片店不敵數碼時代洪流，現時全港擁有12間分店的CD Warehouse顯得頑強不屈。負責人黃先生直認現時銷量上不如九十年代，但唱片市場「成件事都係健康既」，又謂經營唱片店「每個人都有生存空間，睇佢本事」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2222515/org/20419a3fec727e2037c2af9b6c4f7d84.JPG/JronOGY91Wbugf6suKQ-IQsTfVi2CuOkOJMMcjiTDHI?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2222515%2Forg%2F20419a3fec727e2037c2af9b6c4f7d84.JPG%2FJronOGY91Wbugf6suKQ-IQsTfVi2CuOkOJMMcjiTDHI%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=ba0aeda6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港樂壇曾經粒粒巨星，Beyond、譚詠麟、張國榮、梅艷芳、陳百強、四大天王等等，唱片一出，銷量衝上多個白金。九十年代唱片由黑膠轉光碟，是唱片銷量達最高峰時期，大大小小的唱片店比比皆是。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2222540/org/ecacb2f9e61b76da502963d0b11412f8.JPG/ZW-BcWuhaR5SIvKHZkFUozErLkgUy0KG6hrbYOoa22A?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2222540%2Forg%2Fecacb2f9e61b76da502963d0b11412f8.JPG%2FZW-BcWuhaR5SIvKHZkFUozErLkgUy0KG6hrbYOoa22A%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=3bdbf96b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後來隨着翻版及MP3的打擊，光碟銷量大受打擊，加上現時線上音樂串流服務盛行，買唱片對大部份人來說並無需要，令唱片銷量大跌、唱片舖大量倒閉。作為國際連鎖的HMV先是謀求轉型，靠耳機業務苦撐，如今耳機銷量亦因手機制式改變而下跌，撐不下去決定自願清盤。<br />\n<br />\nCD Warehouse成立至今超過20年，由小店發展至目前全港擁最多分店、最大型的連銷唱片店。負責人黃先生表示，「銷量當然冇十幾二十年前咁賣，但成件事都係健康」。<br />\n<br />\n九十年代是唱片業界的高峰，他指「當年靠呢個行業養起好多人，全港有好多CD舖」，後來唱片舖減少，但生存下來的「所有舖頭都有一定實力」。黃認為「香港歌手都賣得」，打破坊間認為香港歌手唔賣得的說法，關鍵只是好壞怎麼衝量。他說，現時新人一般有過千銷量，較受歡迎的新人亦能賣出數千唱片，知名度高的依然過萬，「CD對某啲人嚟講係重要嘅，digital（數位）都緊要，但依家都係有人買CD」。他更指出，數位下載一年可能只帶來數百元的收益，遠遠不如光碟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2222541/org/7716c1bae528e337b76003697750be24.JPG/9r6--0hDgZKjvt6jIF1sU721XZkj7CPLFwXQwBcF0MA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2222541%2Forg%2F7716c1bae528e337b76003697750be24.JPG%2F9r6--0hDgZKjvt6jIF1sU721XZkj7CPLFwXQwBcF0MA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=c3a25b15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他認為唱片市場仍然存在，存亡在於經營的方式，例如信和的唱片店賣韓星商品生意很好，一些小店賣粵曲生意亦不俗，而CD Warehouse無論唱片、電影、配件都業務都十分理想，「每個人都有生存空間，睇佢本事，所以我呢一刻覺得幾好，同以前比較CD梗係差啲，但其他方面都有增長。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2222545/org/fd7443e3159adfff8804b246179d2949.jpg/rcQJiA36UjXd6ARSwJoNUzYzvp11JdHV6oeUOuqHlDo?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2222545%2Forg%2Ffd7443e3159adfff8804b246179d2949.jpg%2FrcQJiA36UjXd6ARSwJoNUzYzvp11JdHV6oeUOuqHlDo%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=ecf5a393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現時唱片仍是CD Warehouse的主要業務，黃認為唱片「其實一路都進步緊」，唱片規格不斷提升，令用家容易享受音樂，而DVD、Blu-ray、4K及數位同樣重要。<br />\n<br />\n此外，耳機仍是配件業務的一環，但不會構成致命的影響，AirPods或其他藍牙耳機只是令耳機種類增加，銷量分佈不同。"},{"pid":"ae1c79b4031f0be51b3832645d9b39bcde48fde1","tid":946365,"uid":60635,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:59:33.000Z","msg":"CD warehouse價錢合理D，其他果兩間美版碟賣到日版價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922bac2bcee6b470d072c0a2a637a3c784b61780","tid":946365,"uid":17646,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"ae1c79b4031f0be51b3832645d9b39bcde48fde1","tid":946365,"uid":60635,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:59:33.000Z","msg":"CD warehouse價錢合理D，其他果兩間美版碟賣到日版價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T13:03:09.000Z","msg":"合理好多,地點又方便"},{"pid":"ab18264d9a95b34ddd32db380baf002d64a888c7","tid":946365,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T13:10:18.000Z","msg":"hmv 快雷射都好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實幾懷疑點解雷射執極都仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c96e9f8699fc863c9dd9df04d88f84ab1a4af2e","tid":946365,"uid":16676,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T13:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Agp0qOq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgp0qOq.png&h=f36f0fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[hmv] 竟然快過[節拍鐳射]執笠<br />\n其實都好意外下<br />\n<br />\n照計[節拍鐳射]執先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07dfb77566dd8df3f717f5f068eef891c9a95fb","tid":946365,"uid":81113,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"3c96e9f8699fc863c9dd9df04d88f84ab1a4af2e","tid":946365,"uid":16676,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T13:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Agp0qOq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgp0qOq.png&h=f36f0fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[hmv] 竟然快過[節拍鐳射]執笠<br />\n其實都好意外下<br />\n<br />\n照計[節拍鐳射]執先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T13:20:58.000Z","msg":"呢間仆街野，淘寶10蚊貨賣$110，仲要寫係清貨價"},{"pid":"a6eb416c7ff2776f24ec2a900673e68d30ef1e42","tid":946365,"uid":133130,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:00:26.000Z","msg":"hmv貴過CD warehouse好多啦<br />\n講真你d歌係有料嘅 就算有kkbox嗰類apps都大把人買正版碟啦<br />\n